# [claude-code 2026-04-26] S45.5/F3: track Piper voice models with git-lfs.
# Run `git lfs install` once per machine before adding *.onnx weights.
# Without this filter, ~60MB binaries would be committed inline and bloat the
# repo + break GitHub's 100MB push cap.

*.onnx filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.onnx.json filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
